  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paper Planet</strong> is a doodly planet-defender roguelike, with Flash-inspired visuals. Born from a love of my childhood favorite Flash games, and modern roguelikes I've sunk countless hours into, taking the best of both planets. Uh..? of both <i>worlds</i>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/634ddedb9ccf02737f849af6dbfb1120.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/634ddedb9ccf02737f849af6dbfb1120.webm?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/634ddedb9ccf02737f849af6dbfb1120.mp4?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/881536bf61d8a64ce38265c5327c1ac4.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/881536bf61d8a64ce38265c5327c1ac4.webm?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/881536bf61d8a64ce38265c5327c1ac4.mp4?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Face down <strong>unique enemies</strong>, with increasingly difficult behaviors and varied attack patterns as each run progresses. Try out <strong>different game modes</strong> and challenges. <strong>Paper Planet</strong> is designed <u>STAY</u> interesting no matter how long you play it! Play with friends in <strong>local co-op</strong> to <i>really</i> push the limits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/0e851b57d9841e3c848b4f9437fd7818.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/0e851b57d9841e3c848b4f9437fd7818.webm?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/0e851b57d9841e3c848b4f9437fd7818.mp4?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/a3bcb89d50689421c56f285e330fbc77.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/a3bcb89d50689421c56f285e330fbc77.webm?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/a3bcb89d50689421c56f285e330fbc77.mp4?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Items BUILT to synergize</strong>! Create massive swarms of bee-bullets, walls of electricity, or teleporting rocket bombs! Every item in <strong>Paper Planet</strong> is made to work with <u>every other</u> item, creating a near infinite number of different combinations to discover!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/4f95219442a7234880abb69480169e32.webp?t=1728942852\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/4f95219442a7234880abb69480169e32.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=60 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/2920822b3b251d9dd85fc85b3509c6c6.poster.avif?t=1728942852\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/2920822b3b251d9dd85fc85b3509c6c6.webm?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1504250/extras/2920822b3b251d9dd85fc85b3509c6c6.mp4?t=1728942852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Showdown against <strong>fun and weird Bosses</strong>. Learn their distinct personalities before overcoming their specialized combat mechanics. Whether you're chasing a high score, risking it all on an overpowered Cursed Item build, or hunting for new and unexpected item combinations.</p>",
